name: Senka Justice - Guan Yun
desc: If only your opponent controls monsters: You can Special Summon this card (from your hand). Other "Senka" monsters you control cannot be targeted by your opponent's effects. If your opponent controls more monsters than you: You can target 1 monster your opponent controls; destroy that target. You can only use this effect of "Senka Justice - Guan Yun" once per turn.
